|flags = Smart switch, PoE+ switch, LACP, SNMP, MSTP, RSTP, heatsink, fan, metal case, |tpfirmware = OpenWrt |availability = Discontinued |eoldate = 2017 |fccapprovdate = |estreldate = |price = |reldate = |newegg = |upc = |ean = |asin = B01MCVF7KB |asin_country = |asin2 = |asin_country2 = |countrymanuf = China |powledcolor = |connactled = |spdledcolor = |leddupcolor = |dimmin = |weight = }}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== *"H3C 1920-8G-POE+ VER.A" is silkscreened on the main board. *"PSE BOARD_BCM59121_8 VER.A" is silkscreened on the PoE board. *[https://svanheule.net/switches/hpe_1920_series ''HPE 1920 Series'' on '''svanheule.net''' Wiki] :Switch (WEB-Managed, 8x 1GbE + 2x SFP ports, Fanless, Rack-mounting, 19") [[:Category:H3C|H3C]] is a subsidiary of [[:Category:HP|HP]] (which completed its acquisition with [[:Category:3Com|3Com]] in April 2010) ===Specifications=== *Processor: [[Realtek]] RTL8380M Multi-Layer Managed Switch :Controller with Embedded MIPS 4KEc @500MHz *Co-processor: [[Nuvoton]] [https://www.nuvoton.com/products/microcontrollers/arm-cortex-m0-mcus/m051-base-series/m0516lde/?__locale=en M0516LDE] to manage PoE *Flash/RAM: 32MB (SPI NOR) Flash, 128MB RAM (DDR3) *LAN: 8x Gigabit (RJ45) 802.3at PoE Ethernet ports, *SFP: 2x GbE SFP slots *PoE: 802.3af (PoE), 802.3at (PoE+), 180W PoE budget :20Gbps switching capacity, Rack mountable (1U, 19") ==Links of Interest== *[https://h20195.www2.hpe.com/v2/default.aspx?cc=nz&lc=en&oid=6783358 Product documentation] ==Flashing== {{Flashnotice}} ===Flashing OpenWrt=== {{OpenWrt |techdata = https://openwrt.org/toh/hwdata/hpe/hpe_1920-8g-poe-180w_jg922a |wikipage = |forumpage = |forumpage2 = |forumpage3 = |github = |target = realtek |subtarget = rtl838x |arch = mips_4kec |support_started_version = 23.05.0 |current_supported_version = auto |unsupportedfuncntions = SFP partially supported |comment = }} Please insert instructions here ==Pictures==
